---
const services = [
  {
    id: 'invisible',
    label: 'Ortodoncia Invisible',
    color: 'sky',
    icon: `<svg viewBox="0 0 64 64" class="w-10 h-10" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <rect x="10" y="16" width="44" height="34" rx="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" fill="none" stroke-dasharray="6 3"/>
      <path d="M20 28 Q32 22 44 28 Q32 36 20 28Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.2"/>
      <circle cx="32" cy="28" r="5" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.6"/>
    </svg>`,
    description:
      'Alinea tus dientes de forma discreta, cómoda y estética con alineadores transparentes removibles. La ortodoncia invisible es ideal para quienes buscan resultados efectivos sin usar brackets visibles y con mayor facilidad de higiene.',
    highlight: 'Pionero en el Eje Cafetero',
    tags: ['Discreta', 'Removible', 'Cómoda', 'Estética'],
  },
  {
    id: 'convencional',
    label: 'Ortodoncia Convencional',
    color: 'blue',
    icon: `<svg viewBox="0 0 64 64" class="w-10 h-10" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <rect x="10" y="14" width="44" height="38" rx="9" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"/>
      <rect x="20" y="24" width="7" height="16" rx="2.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.2"/>
      <rect x="29" y="22" width="7" height="18" rx="2.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.2"/>
      <rect x="38" y="25" width="6" height="13" rx="2.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.2"/>
      <path d="M14 44 Q32 52 50 44" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
    </svg>`,
    description:
      'La ortodoncia convencional con brackets es un tratamiento eficaz y preciso para corregir la posición de los dientes y la mordida. Permite tratar desde casos simples hasta complejos, mejorando la función, la salud oral y la estética de la sonrisa.',
    highlight: 'Casos simples y complejos',
    tags: ['Preciso', 'Eficaz', 'Versátil', 'Accesible'],
  },
  {
    id: 'cirugia',
    label: 'Ortodoncia y Cirugía Maxilofacial',
    color: 'violet',
    icon: `<svg viewBox="0 0 64 64" class="w-10 h-10" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <path d="M32 8 C18 8 12 20 12 30 C12 44 20 54 32 54 C44 54 52 44 52 30 C52 20 46 8 32 8Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" fill="none"/>
      <path d="M22 28 L42 28" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
      <path d="M32 18 L32 40" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
      <circle cx="48" cy="16" r="9" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.15" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
      <path d="M45 16 L47 18 L52 13" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
    </svg>`,
    description:
      'Indicada para pacientes con alteraciones en la posición de los maxilares que requieren un manejo integral. La combinación de ortodoncia y cirugía maxilofacial busca mejorar la función, la armonía facial y la calidad de vida.',
    highlight: 'Manejo integral especializado',
    tags: ['Integral', 'Planificación', 'Armonía Facial', 'Especializado'],
  },
  {
    id: 'blanqueamiento',
    label: 'Blanqueamiento Dental',
    color: 'amber',
    icon: `<svg viewBox="0 0 64 64" class="w-10 h-10" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <path d="M16 20 Q16 10 26 10 Q32 10 32 17 Q32 10 38 10 Q48 10 48 20 Q48 32 32 46 Q16 32 16 20Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linejoin="round" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.1"/>
      <path d="M26 28 L30 32 L38 22" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
      <circle cx="50" cy="14" r="5" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.4"/>
      <path d="M48 12 L50 14 L54 10" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
    </svg>`,
    description:
      'Recupera un tono dental más claro y uniforme de forma segura y controlada. El blanqueamiento dental mejora la apariencia de la sonrisa, siempre bajo valoración profesional para cuidar la salud de tus dientes.',
    highlight: 'Seguro y controlado',
    tags: ['Estético', 'Seguro', 'Rápido', 'Profesional'],
  },
  {
    id: 'higiene',
    label: 'Higiene Oral',
    color: 'emerald',
    icon: `<svg viewBox="0 0 64 64" class="w-10 h-10" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <rect x="18" y="14" width="8" height="28" rx="4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.1"/>
      <path d="M22 14 Q26 8 30 14" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" fill="none"/>
      <circle cx="42" cy="36" r="13" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" fill="none"/>
      <path d="M42 28 L42 44 M34 36 L50 36" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
    </svg>`,
    description:
      'La higiene oral profesional es clave para mantener dientes y encías sanos. Ayuda a eliminar placa y sarro, prevenir enfermedades periodontales y mantener tu sonrisa limpia y saludable, especialmente si estás en tratamiento de ortodoncia.',
    highlight: 'Esencial en ortodoncia',
    tags: ['Preventivo', 'Saludable', 'Profesional', 'Esencial'],
  },
];

const colorMap: Record<string, string> = {
  sky:     'text-sky-600 bg-sky-50 border-sky-200 hover:border-sky-400 hover:bg-sky-50',
  blue:    'text-blue-600 bg-blue-50 border-blue-200 hover:border-blue-400 hover:bg-blue-50',
  violet:  'text-violet-600 bg-violet-50 border-violet-200 hover:border-violet-400 hover:bg-violet-50',
  amber:   'text-amber-600 bg-amber-50 border-amber-200 hover:border-amber-400 hover:bg-amber-50',
  emerald: 'text-emerald-600 bg-emerald-50 border-emerald-200 hover:border-emerald-400 hover:bg-emerald-50',
};
const badgeMap: Record<string, string> = {
  sky:     'bg-sky-100 text-sky-700',
  blue:    'bg-blue-100 text-blue-700',
  violet:  'bg-violet-100 text-violet-700',
  amber:   'bg-amber-100 text-amber-700',
  emerald: 'bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700',
};
---

<section id="servicios" class="relative py-24 bg-gradient-to-b from-sky-50 via-white to-sky-50 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute left-1/2 top-0 -translate-x-1/2 w-[700px] h-64 bg-sky-200/30 rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 glass border border-sky-200 rounded-full px-4 py-2 mb-4 reveal">
        <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-sky-500 rounded-full animate-pulse"></span>
        <span class="text-sky-600 text-xs font-medium tracking-widest uppercase">Lo que ofrecemos</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-800 reveal" style="transition-delay:0.1s">
        Nuestros <span class="gradient-text">Servicios</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-slate-500 max-w-xl mx-auto reveal" style="transition-delay:0.2s">
        Tratamientos de ortodoncia personalizados con tecnología de vanguardia y más de 30 años de experiencia.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Service cards -->
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 stagger">
      {services.map((s, i) => (
        <div
          class={`group relative glass border rounded-3xl p-7 transition-all duration-400 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-2xl reveal-scale ${colorMap[s.color]}`}
          style={`transition-delay:${i * 0.1}s`}
        >
          <!-- Icon -->
          <div class={`w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5 transition-transform group-hover:scale-110 duration-300 ${colorMap[s.color]}`}>
            <span set:html={s.icon} />
          </div>

          <!-- Badge -->
          <span class={`inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium mb-3 ${badgeMap[s.color]}`}>
            {s.highlight}
          </span>

          <!-- Title -->
          <h3 class="text-slate-800 font-display font-semibold text-xl mb-3 leading-snug group-hover:text-inherit">
            {s.label}
          </h3>

          <!-- Description -->
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-5 group-hover:text-slate-600 transition-colors">
            {s.description}
          </p>

          <!-- Tags -->
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
            {s.tags.map(tag => (
              <span class="text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-slate-100 text-slate-500 border border-slate-200">
                {tag}
              </span>
            ))}
          </div>

          <!-- Hover arrow -->
          <div class="absolute top-6 right-6 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-current" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.293 9.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 12.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 011.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" transform="rotate(-90, 10, 10)"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
      ))}

      <!-- CTA card -->
      <div class="group glass border border-sky-200 rounded-3xl p-7 bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-50 to-white hover:from-sky-100 hover:border-sky-400 transition-all duration-400 hover:-translate-y-2 flex flex-col justify-between reveal-scale" style="transition-delay:0.5s">
        <div>
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-sky-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-sky-600" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"/>
              <line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"/>
              <line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"/>
              <line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-slate-800 font-display font-semibold text-xl mb-3">¿Listo para transformar tu sonrisa?</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Agenda una valoración con el Dr. Ramiro Mejía y recibe un plan personalizado.
          </p>
        </div>
        <a
          href="#agenda"
          class="mt-8 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 w-full py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-sky-500 to-sky-600 hover:from-sky-400 hover:to-sky-500 text-white font-semibold rounded-2xl shadow-lg shadow-sky-200 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105"
        >
          Agendar Valoración
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 5.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L12.586 11H5a1 1 0 110-2h7.586l-2.293-2.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
